1. *Vile* su prekrasne i elegantne životinje. (The *deer* are beautiful and elegant animals.)
2. Baka je imala vikendicu na obroncima *vila*. (Grandma had a cottage on the slopes of the *mountain range*.)
3. Vozio sam kroz gustu *vilu* dok nisam došao do jezera. (I drove through a thick *forest* until I reached the lake.)
4. Moramo očistiti ove *vile* iz kanalizacije. (We need to clean these *sewage pipes*.)
5. *Vila* je uzela moj dah kad sam ušao u nju. (The *house* took my breath away when I entered it.)
6. Sanjam o tome da živim u *vili* na obali mora. (I dream of living in a *mansion* on the seaside.)
7. *Vilama* su potrebne snažne temelje kako bi mogle izdržati jake vjetrove. (The *towers* need strong foundations to withstand strong winds.)
8. *Vile* su se skrivale među drvećem dok smo prolazili pored njih. (The *fairies* were hiding among the trees as we passed by them.)
9. Ne smijemo dopustiti da *vile* unište našu baštu. (We must not allow *weeds* to destroy our garden.)
10. Želio sam kupiti *vilu* ali nisam imao dovoljno novca. (I wanted to buy a *racket* but I didn't have enough money.)